ttack the CISC problems, frequency of transistors. You=E2=80=99ve got perfo=
rmance for free. And if that gap was in a reasonable frame, you know, if it=
=E2=80=99s less than 2x, hey, in a Moore=E2=80=99s Law=E2=80=99s term that=
